rComments: Syllabus and class contents are easy to understand. but since theres no textbook used, 100% of concentration should be paid otherwise you wont get it in any other way. Really a lot of tests, but they are fun. Tough grader btw.

Kevin appreciates participation! The more you participate in lectures and projects the better. But your marks will also rely on working in groups so be a team player. Really cool guy and willing to set up a time outside of class to help with anything you're struggling with. Probably one of the funniest people I know.

rComments: Great instructor.  For the most part he knows how to keep the ball rolling although he sometimes fumbles it and can be boring.  But he is always extremely helpful and rewards attendance/hard work with good marks.  Don't expect to coast through this class.  Only thing is sometimes I feel he tries a little to hard to be 'cool'.  Tells great stories!
